    <author initials="M." surname="Douglass" fullname="Michael Douglass">
      <organization>Bedework Commercial Services</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="11" month="July" year="2022"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a set of new properties for iCalendar and
   extends the use of existing ones.  Their primary purpose is to align
   the same set of features between the JSCalendar and iCalendar
   formats, but the new definitions also aim to be useful within just
   the iCalendar format.

	 </t>
